'''Black demons''' are large [[demons]] that inhabit various [[List of dungeons|dungeons]] throughout [[Gielinor]]. They are weak to [[demonbane weapons]]; as with most demons, they are also weak to [[magical]] attacks.

A [[Black demon (The Grand Tree)|unique black demon]] is defeated during [[The Grand Tree]]. This demon can be re-fought in the [[Nightmare Zone]] after the quest has been completed. [[Black demon (The Scar)|Black demons]] as well as [[Scarred black demon]]s can be found in [[The Scar]].

[[Demonic gorilla]]s, [[Balfrug Kreeyath]], [[Skotizo]], [[Porazdir]], and [[Kolodion]]'s final form can also be killed in place of black demons in regards to a Slayer task.

Black demons can be [[safespot]]ted with [[Magic]], [[Ranged]], or [[halberd]]s in all of their locations.

